header.value: the quality bitmask for each fiber pixel

hdu8.name: SLITMAP
hdu8.description: slitmap table describing fiber positions for this exposure

fiberid.name: fiberid
fiberid.description: number of the fiber along the slithead

spectrographid.name: spectrographid
spectrographid.description: the spectrograph id number, either 1, 2 or 3

blockid.name: blockid
blockid.description: the ID label of the block along the slit

finblock.name: finblock
finblock.description: the fiber number within the v-groove block

targettype.name: targettype
targettype.description: the type of fiber, either science, standard or sky

ifulabel.name: ifulabel
ifulabel.description: an ID label for the telescope + sector

finifu.name: finifu
finifu.description: a running fiber number within the IFU from 1 to N

telescope.name: telescope
telescope.description: the name of the telescope; Sci, Spec, SkyE/W for science, standards, or skies

xpmm.name: xpmm
xpmm.description: the x coordinate in mm of the fiber relative to the centroid

ypmm.name: ypmm
ypmm.description: the y coordinate in mm of the fiber relative to the centroid

ringnum.name: ringnum
ringnum.description: the number of the IFU ring the fiber belongs to

orig_ifulabel.name: orig_ifulabel
orig_ifulabel.description: the original IFU label from the Excel document. WRONG! DO NOT USE!

orig_slitlabel.name: orig_slitlabel
orig_slitlabel.description: the original slitblock label from the Excel document. WRONG! DO NOT USE!

finsector.name: finsector
finsector.description: the original fiber number within the IFU sector

fmap.name: fmap
fmap.description: the current fiber flow FROM:TO from the IFU position to the SLIT position

ypix_b.name: ypix_b
ypix_b.description: the y coordinate in pixels of the fiber at column 2000 for channel b

ypix_r.name: ypix_r
ypix_r.description: the y coordinate in pixels of the fiber at column 2000 for channel r

ypix_z.name: ypix_z
ypix_z.description: the y coordinate in pixels of the fiber at column 2000 for channel z

ra.name: ra
ra.description: the right ascension of the fiber in J2000

dec.name: dec
dec.description: the declination of the fiber in J2000
